&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The position is based in Newark with a hybrid work schedule where staff members work in the office Tuesdays and Wednesdays.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:320,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
